"This contest has started accruing tickets (or is closed) — its schedule and "
"rules are locked; only the text/display fields were saved."
msgstr "此抽奖活动已开始累计抽奖券（或已关闭）—— 其日程与规则已锁定；仅保存了文本/展示字段。"

