msgid ""
"No jump route within range — try a longer-range hull/JDC, fewer avoided "
"systems/waypoints, or drop ‘dockable only’."
msgstr "射程内没有跳跃路线 —— 试试射程更远的船体/更高的 JDC、减少规避星系/途经点，或取消“仅可停靠”。"

