"required."
msgstr "这条警报将触达 %(count)s 名飞行员，需要进行大范围受众确认。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
#| msgid "P0 · Raw resource"
msgid "Raw resource"
msgstr "原始资源"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Pulled straight from a planet by an Extractor Control Unit."
msgstr "由采集控制单元直接从行星上抽取。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"The 15 raw materials. You never sell these — you refine them on-planet into "
"P1. Extraction rate depends on your ECU program and the planet's resource "
"hotspots, so it's the one number you should tune to your colony."
msgstr ""
"15 种原始材料。你不会直接出售它们——而是在行星上精炼成 P1。采集速率取决于你的 ECU "
"程序和行星上的资源热点，因此这是唯一需要针对自己殖民地调整的数值。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Extractor Control Unit (ECU) + extractor heads"
msgstr "采集控制单元（ECU）+ 采集头"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
#| msgid "P1 · Processed material"
msgid "Processed material"
msgstr "加工材料"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "One P0 refined in a Basic Industry Facility."
msgstr "在基础工业设施中精炼一种 P0 得到。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"15 processed materials. A Basic Industry Facility turns 3,000 of one P0 into"
" 20 P1 every 30 minutes. P1 is the first thing worth selling, and the "
"feedstock for everything above it."
msgstr ""
"15 种加工材料。一座基础工业设施每 30 分钟把 3,000 单位某种 P0 转化成 20 单位 P1。P1 "
"是第一种值得出售的产物，也是上层所有产物的原料。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Basic Industry Facility (BIF)"
msgstr "基础工业设施（BIF）"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
#| msgid "P2 · Refined commodity"
msgid "Refined commodity"
msgstr "精炼商品"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Two P1 combined in an Advanced Industry Facility."
msgstr "在高级工业设施中把两种 P1 合成得到。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"Refined commodities combine two P1 inputs. These are the bread-and-butter of"
" profitable PI — good ISK/m³ and steady demand (Coolant, Mechanical Parts, "
"Consumer Electronics, Enriched Uranium…)."
msgstr ""
"精炼商品由两种 P1 原料合成。它们是 PI 盈利的主力——ISK/m³ 表现不错，需求稳定（Coolant、Mechanical "
"Parts、Consumer Electronics、Enriched Uranium…）。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Advanced Industry Facility (AIF)"
msgstr "高级工业设施（AIF）"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
#| msgid "P3 · Specialised commodity"
msgid "Specialised commodity"
msgstr "特种商品"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "Several P2 combined into a high-value good."
msgstr "由多种 P2 合成的高价值物品。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"Specialised commodities (Robotics, Coolant→…, Guidance Systems, Transcranial"
" Microcontrollers…). High value per unit but they need a multi-planet supply"
" chain or a market to buy the P2 inputs."
msgstr ""
"特种商品（Robotics、Coolant→…、Guidance Systems、Transcranial "
"Microcontrollers…）。单位价值高，但需要多行星供应链，或者需要能买到 P2 原料的市场。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
#| msgid "P4 · Advanced commodity"
msgid "Advanced commodity"
msgstr "高级商品"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid "The end of the chain — mixes P3 (and some P1) into strategic goods."
msgstr "产业链的终点——把 P3（以及部分 P1）混合成战略物资。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
msgid ""
"Advanced commodities (Nano-Factory, Broadcast Node, Self-Harmonising Power "
"Core, Wetware Mainframe) feed sovereignty structures and capital "
"construction. Only worth it with a dedicated multi-character operation."
msgstr ""
"高级商品（Nano-Factory、Broadcast Node、Self-Harmonising Power Core、Wetware "
"Mainframe）供给主权建筑和 capital 建造。只有投入多角色专职运营才划算。"

#: apps/planetary/constants.py
#| msgid "My production plans"
msgid "High-Tech Production Plant"
msgstr "高科技生产厂"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Which of your pilots will run this colony network. Used to label the plan "
"and to match imported colonies — nothing is changed in-game."
msgstr "您的哪位飞行员将运营这个殖民地网络。用于标记计划并匹配导入的殖民地 — 游戏内不会有任何改动。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Pricing hub"
msgstr "定价枢纽"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Where you'll sell. Prices and profit are estimated against this hub. Jita is"
" the most liquid and the safest default."
msgstr "您将在哪里出售。价格和利润以此枢纽为基准估算。Jita 流动性最高，是最安全的默认选择。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "e.g. Jita P2 Coolant run"
msgstr "例如 Jita P2 Coolant 批次"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "e.g. Amamake (optional)"
msgstr "例如 Amamake（可选）"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Anything you want to remember about this setup."
msgstr "关于此设置您想记住的任何内容。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "A short name you'll recognise in your plan list."
msgstr "一个您在计划列表中能认出的简短名称。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"What you want out of PI. This tunes the recommendations and the guidance."
msgstr "您希望从 PI 中获得什么。这会调整推荐和指导。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"The system (or staging) you'll run this from. Optional, for your notes."
msgstr "您将从哪个星系（或集结点）运营此计划。可选，供您备注。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"How many planets you'll dedicate (1–6). Alpha clones are limited; Omega "
"pilots can run more with the right skills."
msgstr "您将投入多少颗行星（1–6）。Alpha 克隆有限制；Omega 飞行员在具备合适技能时可运营更多。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Where you'll set up. Nullsec/wormhole planets yield more but cost you "
"hauling and danger — this is context for the guidance, not a hard rule."
msgstr "您将在哪里建立。Nullsec/虫洞行星产出更高，但会带来运输成本和危险 — 这是指导的背景信息，而非硬性规则。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Customs office (POCO) tax on export, as a %. In hostile space this can be "
"high — check the POCO before you commit."
msgstr "出口时的海关办公室（POCO）税率，以 % 计。在敌对空间这个数字可能高得离谱 —— 动手之前先看清 POCO。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "POCO tax on importing materials to a factory planet, as a %."
msgstr "向工厂行星进口材料时的 POCO 税率，以 % 计。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Market sales tax when you sell (%). Scales down with Accounting."
msgstr "你出售时的市场销售税（%）。随 Accounting 技能等级降低。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Broker fee on sell orders (%). 0 if you only sell to buy orders."
msgstr "卖单的经纪人费用（%）。如果你只卖给买单，就填 0。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"ISK per m³ to move goods to the hub. 0 if you haul yourself. Applied only "
"when the export strategy is 'haul to hub'."
msgstr "将货物运至枢纽的每 m³ ISK 成本。若自行运输则为 0。仅当出口策略为 'haul to hub' 时适用。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "If you use corp buyback, the percent of Jita sell it pays."
msgstr "如果你走军团 buyback，它支付的价格相当于 Jita 卖价的百分之多少。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Planning assumption: P0 units/hour on one extraction planet. Tune it to your"
" real colonies for accuracy."
msgstr "规划假设：单颗开采行星每小时的 P0 单位数。为提高准确性，请根据您的真实殖民地进行调整。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"How often you'll reset extractors and haul. Low effort favours simple, long-"
"cycle setups."
msgstr "您重置提取器和运输的频率。低投入偏向简单、长周期的设置。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "What you'll do with the output — it changes which fees apply."
msgstr "您将如何处理产出 — 这会改变适用哪些费用。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Who can see this plan. Private is only you."
msgstr "谁可以查看此计划。私密仅限您自己。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "— select a pilot —"
msgstr "— 选择一位飞行员 —"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Enter a percentage between 0 and 100."
msgstr "请输入 0 到 100 之间的百分比。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "A pilot can run between 1 and 6 planets."
msgstr "一位飞行员可运营 1 到 6 颗行星。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Default pricing hub"
msgstr "默认定价枢纽"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Corp priority products"
msgstr "公司优先产品"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid ""
"Comma-separated PI product names the corp wants pilots to make (e.g. "
"Coolant, Mechanical Parts, Robotics). They get a badge in the "
"recommendations."
msgstr ""
"公司希望飞行员制造的 PI 产品名称（以逗号分隔，例如 Coolant、Mechanical Parts、Robotics）。它们在推荐中会获得徽章。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "e.g. lowsec staging, home constellation"
msgstr "例如 lowsec 集结点、母星座"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Master switch. Off hides the whole planner from pilots."
msgstr "总开关。关闭后将对飞行员隐藏整个规划器。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "A label for this config (only you see it)."
msgstr "此配置的标签（仅您可见）。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Starting extraction assumption for new plans."
msgstr "新计划的初始开采假设。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Percent of Jita sell the corp buyback pays, for plans that use it."
msgstr "军团 buyback 支付的价格相当于 Jita 卖价的百分比，适用于使用它的方案。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Free text: where the corp suggests running PI."
msgstr "自由文本：公司建议在哪里运营 PI。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "A short note shown to pilots about what the corp needs."
msgstr "向飞行员显示的关于公司需求的简短说明。"

#: apps/planetary/forms.py
msgid "Default sharing for newly-created plans."
msgstr "新建计划的默认共享设置。"

