msgstr "该飞行员没有 FORCA Command Grid 账户。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Ask them to sign in with EVE SSO to start earning tickets."
msgstr "请让他们使用 EVE SSO 登录，以开始赚取抽奖券。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "This character isn't linked to a FORCA account."
msgstr "该角色未关联到 FORCA 账户。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Sign in with EVE SSO to enrol and start earning tickets."
msgstr "使用 EVE SSO 登录以报名并开始赚取抽奖券。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "You've been excluded from this contest by leadership."
msgstr "你已被领导层排除在本次比赛之外。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Contact a director if you believe this is a mistake."
msgstr "如果你认为这是误操作，请联系 Director。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "You haven't connected an ESI token yet."
msgstr "你还没有连接 ESI token。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Connect your ESI token to start earning raffle tickets."
msgstr "连接你的 ESI token 以开始赚取抽奖券。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Your ESI token has expired or been revoked."
msgstr "你的 ESI token 已过期或被撤销。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Reconnect your ESI token to keep earning tickets."
msgstr "重新连接你的 ESI token 以继续赚取抽奖券。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Your ESI token is missing a scope this contest needs."
msgstr "你的 ESI token 缺少本次比赛所需的 scope。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Re-authorise with the required scopes to earn tickets."
msgstr "请使用所需的 scope 重新授权以赚取抽奖券。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Only recognised corporation pilots can take part."
msgstr "只有已认证的军团飞行员才能参加。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Make sure your main is in the corp and re-sync your affiliation."
msgstr "请确保你的主角色在军团内，并重新同步你的所属关系。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "You're eligible — fly, earn tickets and check your progress."
msgstr "你符合资格 — 出击、赚取抽奖券并查看你的进度。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
msgid "Sign in with EVE SSO to take part in the raffle."
msgstr "使用 EVE SSO 登录以参加抽奖。"

#: apps/raffle/eligibility.py
