msgstr "实战演练带你一步步从停靠,到在真实舰队中 hold tackle。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Someone in your corner."
msgstr "有人在你这边。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"A name you can ping without feeling like you're bothering the whole corp."
msgstr "一个你可以 ping 而不必觉得在打扰整个军团的人。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Earn as you learn."
msgstr "边学边赚。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Completed exercises can pay ISK, points and recognition — see below."
msgstr "完成演练可获得 ISK、积分和荣誉 — 见下文。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Why mentor as a Veteran"
msgstr "为何以老兵身份担任导师"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Build the fleet you want to fly with."
msgstr "打造你想与之并肩作战的舰队。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Every Cadet you train is another competent pilot on comms next month."
msgstr "你训练的每位学员,下个月都会成为语音频道里又一名能干的飞行员。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Recognition that sticks."
msgstr "长久留存的荣誉。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Mentor badges, certifications and standing on the leadership board."
msgstr "导师徽章、认证以及在领导层榜单上的排名。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Light touch, real impact."
msgstr "轻投入,真影响。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"You pick your areas, your timezone and your pace — the Grid handles the "
"matching and the paperwork."
msgstr "你选择自己的领域、时区和节奏 — Grid 负责配对和文书工作。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Give back what you were given."
msgstr "回馈你曾经得到的。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Every veteran here was once the confused newbro asking where the undock "
"button is."
msgstr "这里每位老兵都曾是那个不知所措、问出站按钮在哪的新人。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Register a role"
msgstr "注册角色"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Sign up as a Cadet, a Veteran Mentor, or both. Tell us your goals, areas and"
" timezone."
msgstr "报名成为学员、资深导师,或两者兼任。告诉我们你的目标、领域和时区。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Get matched"
msgstr "获得配对"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"The Grid suggests best-fit pairings by area, timezone and goals. You approve"
" — nobody is forced together."
msgstr "Grid 会按领域、时区和目标推荐最契合的配对。由你批准 — 没有人会被强行凑对。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Run Field Exercises"
msgstr "开展实战演练"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Work through a Track together — first fit, first fleet, first ratting site —"
" and debrief each one."
msgstr "一起完成一条路线 — 第一次装配、第一次舰队、第一个 ratting 站点 — 并逐一复盘。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Earn recognition"
msgstr "赢得荣誉"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Completed exercises are validated, then Cadet and Mentor both collect their "
"rewards."
msgstr "完成的演练经过验证后,学员和导师都会领取各自的奖励。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "What you earn"
msgstr "你能获得什么"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Progress is real recognition, not a participation ribbon. Depending on how "
"leadership has tuned the programme, completing exercises and certifications "
"can grant:"
msgstr "进步是真正的荣誉,而非参与奖。根据领导层对该计划的调整,完成演练和认证可授予:"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "ISK rewards"
msgstr "ISK 奖励"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Direct payouts for milestones — for the Cadet who did the work and the "
"Mentor who taught it."
msgstr "为里程碑直接发放报酬 — 给完成任务的学员和进行教学的导师。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Points on the corp recognition ledger that count toward your standing."
msgstr "军团荣誉账簿上的积分,计入你的排名。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Badges"
msgstr "徽章"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Tiered mentor and cadet badges that show on your profile and dashboard."
msgstr "分级的导师和学员徽章,显示在你的档案和仪表板上。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Certifications"
msgstr "认证"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Proof you can fly the doctrine, hold tackle, or lead a small gang — "
"recognised corp-wide."
msgstr "证明你能驾驶 doctrine、hold tackle 或带领一支小队 — 全军团认可。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Honest validation &amp; privacy"
msgstr "诚实验证 &amp; 隐私"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Some steps auto-check."
msgstr "部分步骤自动核对。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Where the Grid can confirm a fact from EVE data — a skill trained, a ship "
"owned — it ticks the box for you."
msgstr "凡是 Grid 能从 EVE 数据确认的事实 — 已训练的技能、已拥有的船只 — 都会为你自动打钩。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "The rest is a Mentor sign-off."
msgstr "其余的由导师签核。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"Things a machine can't judge — \"did the debrief, showed up, gets it\" — "
"your Mentor confirms by hand. No gaming it."
msgstr "机器无法判断的事情 — \"做了复盘、到场了、领会了\" — 由你的导师手动确认。无法作弊。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "ESI is opt-in and minimal."
msgstr "ESI 是自愿授权且最小化的。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid ""
"We only ask for a scope when an exercise genuinely needs it, and never more "
"than that. You can join and progress plenty without granting any."
msgstr "只有当某项演练确实需要时,我们才会请求某个权限范围,绝不超出。即使不授予任何权限,你也能加入并取得大量进展。"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "Commitment:"
msgstr "投入:"

#: templates/mentorship/landing.html
msgid "a few hours a week is plenty — set your own pace, pause any time."
msgstr "每周几个小时就够了 — 按自己的节奏来,随时可暂停。"

